abstract: >-
  Citegeist is a Zotero 7+ plugin (compatible with Zotero 8) that embeds citation intelligence
  directly into the reference manager. It displays citation counts,
  field-weighted citation impact, percentile rankings, citation trends,
  journal-level metrics, and journal ranking lists (UTD24, FT50, ABDC,
  AJG) for any paper with a DOI, and provides a citation network browser
  for discovering and importing related works — all powered by the
  OpenAlex open bibliometric index.
